### Personal reflection
It's a great book, but I haven't found a practical use for it yet - maybe I will someday. Overall, it's especially useful for people who have to hold high-stakes conversations with employees, clients, or superiors.

### Would I recommend it?
Yes - especially for people who frequently face crucial conversations. There are also tips you can use in everyday chats.

